captions.text: Ro: Hey guys, it’s Ro and my sister Mo!
Mo: Hello!

Ro: We got so many requests from you guys
for which fun game we should play next
Ro: and the most requested thing was…
Mo: What’s in my Mouth?

Mo: For those of you who don’t know about
the What’s in my Mouth challenge,

Mo: It’s when I get to blindfold my sister
and pick 10 different things to

Mo: put into her mouth, and she has to guess
what they are.

Ro: When she was really, really little she
was a really picky eater.

Ro: She only ate bread and cheese… Mo: They’re
the best! Ro: I told her

Ro: to take a grape and put it in between
her teeth, just out of trust,

Ro: to trust me. And I put it right there,
and then I went… Boom!

Mo: And it was good, and now I love grapes.
Ro: She does love grapes.
Mo: But, now it’s payback time for that!
Ro: Oh jeez! Mo: Can you see?
Mo: First thing, I’m gonna do…
Mo: OK, open your mouth. Ready?
Ro: It’s a prune! Mo: Yeah, OK it's a prune!
Mo: They, they help with certain things.

Ro: I got it, 1 thing out of 10, that’s
not bad.
Mo: Next thing on the list.
Ro: Candy, candy, candy!
Mo: Yeah it’s candy!
Ro: What candy boxes have a lid?
Ro: I’m ready. OK
Mo: Get it in there, get it in there. OK.
Ro: Very salty, is it Tuna? Mo: No.
Mo: That was spam.

Ro: Oh Molly! Mo: I don’t think you’ve
ever had that before, so that’s kinda cheating.
Mo: Next thing.
Mo: OK, bite down.
Ro: Oh! That’s relish!

Mo: Yeah, it’s sweet relish! You nailed
that.

Ro: I didn’t realize how strong that is,
like, not on a hotdog or something.
Ro: Like that is really strong!

Mo: Next thing, I think we have something
that you probably haven’t tried before.

Ro: Mmm-mmm! Mo: Yeah, come-on, just… Ro:
Mmm-mmm! Mo: Just open a little!

Ro: It’s some type of a chip… Oh this
is bizarre! Caramel? Something weird.

Ro: It was like a cappuccino, coffee… Mo:
Yeah! Ro: Potato chip.
Mo: Boom, you nailed it!

Mo: Onto number 5, we have… This is one
of my favorites in the kitchen.
Ro: Oh no, it’s not V-8 is it?
Ro: Oh my! OH! OH! Oh, oh, oh! Oh, oh! Oooo-ooo-oooo-ooo!

Ro: That just… GARLIC! Just, just like…
Liquid, just so much garlic!
Ro: Oh god! That was a good one!

Ro: I feel like that’s just, shot my taste
buds. Like, I don’t know if I can taste anything
Ro: after that.

Ro: It’s bubbly… Mo: Yeah. Ro: Carbonated..
Mo: Yeah. Ro: I don’t know… Oh,

Ro: that’s an energy drink! Mo: Yup. Ro:
Yeah, is that red bull?
Mo: It’s Red Bull! Ro: OK!

Mo: So now you’re 5 out of 6, so… Ro:
Woo-hoo! Mo: That’s pretty good.
Ro: OK, that’s a pretty good score!
Mo: OK, we’re gonna do another liquid. OK...
Ro: OOOOH! Tart!

Ro: I’m trying to decide if it’s lemon
or lime.

Mo: Aaaah… Ro: It’s so tart, that I’m…
Mo: It's lemon Juice! Ro: It is?

Mo: It’s the lemon juice, it’s like the
concentrate.
Mo: This is number 8, here we go.

Ro: WHAT? Molly! It’s a… It smells like
bacon… Molly is this a biscuit?
Ro: Is this an animal biscuit?
Mo: Like a dog treat!
Ro: Why did I know what that is?
Mo: Number 9.

Ro: Gosh as long as you don’t do another
dog biscuit!

Ro: Ooooh! Ooooh! Ooooh! Ah! Ah! Ah! Ohhh-ho-ho-ho!
Ohhhhh! It’s so hot!

Ro: Oh my god, that’s hot sauce! Mo: Yeah.
Ro: That has to be, it’s like a pepper!
Mo: Do you want some lemon juice?
Ro: Molly it’s on fire!

Ro: I’m ready for anything after that. I
don’t think I can taste anything anymore,

Ro: like my, my taste buds are completely
destroyed.
Mo: Next we have some…
Mo: Choo-choo-choo-choo-choo! Ro: OK…
Ro: Is this mayonnaise? Mo: Yeah!
Ro: Ohhhh, oh!
Mo: Eeeew! No!

Mo: You got another one, you’re a pro at
this even when you don’t have taste buds.

Mo: OK Rosanna, are you ready for the last
one?
Ro: Ugh, wait, hold on… Oh, my belly, oh!

Ro: Do you hear that? It’s like gurgling.
Molly unintentionally created the
Ro: master cleanse!
Ro: Cotton ball! Mo: Nailed it!

Ro: Whew! Alright, I survived the What’s
in my Mouth challenge! Uh, thank you

Ro: Guys for suggesting that? It was really
fun, and definitely really weird.

Mo: I know I had a blast doing that. Ro: Yeah…
Mo: That was amazing.

Ro: I bet you did, I bet she had a blast doing
that! If you guys have any

Ro: other fun ideas or games that you think
Mo and I should play, leave us a

Ro: comment down below and we’ll check ‘em
out!

Ro: Also, you can click up here… Mo: Or
here. Ro: Yeah, and you can watch our

Ro: previous Vlogs and fun games that we do.
And I will put Mo’s links in

Ro: the description, she has twitter and,
ins… Instagram? Mo: Instagram!

Ro: And Instagram now if you want to follow
her.
Ro: Oh Molly, you’re so pretty! Mo: I know.

Ro: Alright, open your mouth. Really wide,
really wide, because it’s kind of…

Ro: You know, really wide, that’s not wide!
There you go, really wide, really wide.
Ro: Bite down!
Ro: Like when we were little!
Ro: It was a grape!
Ro: Alright, thanks you guys, bye-bye!
